OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day but with a
OL,6,Ffew bright spells, mainly in the east
OL,7,Fin the morning. Frequent showers
OL,8,Ffeeding in from the west. Showers
OL,9,Fheavy at times and forming longer
OL,10,Fspells of rain later. Windy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy throughout
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight with
OL,14,Ffrequent showers, these heavy at times
OL,15,Fand occasionally forming longer spells
OL,16,Fof rain. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
