OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy and breezy with
OL,6,Fshowers, heavy and forming longer
OL,7,Fspells of rain at times. Rain and
OL,8,Fstrong winds gradually easing later in
OL,9,Fthe day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry on Sunday and Monday with some
OL,13,Flong spells of sunshine. Some rain
OL,14,Fspreading northeast later Monday.
OL,15,FCloudy on Tuesday with rain or
OL,16,Fshowers. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
